John Henson (comedian) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Henson_(comedian) 0 John Morris Henson (born July 11, 1967) is an American actor, comedian and talk show host. He was the co-host of ABC's Wipeout with John Anderson, a prime-time game show that ran for 7 seasons. John_Morris_Henson ( born July_11_,_1967 ) is an_American_actor_,_comedian_and_talk show host .
